[32m│[0m ### Analysis                                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **The "prototype pollution protection" messages are just RED HERRINGS** - they are     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m server-generated error strings, NOT actual prototype manipulation failures.            [32m│[0m
