[32m│[0m 3. **This is Python/Flask** - Python dictionaries don't have JavaScript-style          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m prototypes, so `__proto__` keys are just treated as normal dictionary keys             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                        [32m│[0m
