[32m│[0m ### Behavior Analysis                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **GET /page**:                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Always returns: Static form with message "Let the game begin. Good Luck"             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Query parameters are completely ignored                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Only POST requests with `solution` parameter trigger reflection                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                        [32m│[0m
